<br>
The Main Tank is the ONLY one that should be using Taunt/Disarm/Beg/etc...  Until it is time for the 2nd Tank to start building aggro, 3rd Tank, and so on...<br>
<br>
NO ONE but The Main Tank (whether it is 1, 2, 3, etc.) should be taunting the mob until thier turn. <p>Muffuni Falconheal<BR>
